external.description: Strudel is a music live coding environment for the browser, porting the TidalCycles pattern language to JavaScript.
external.title: Strudel REPL

record.text: So this is an interesting way of making music that I was not really aware of until now. Not sure I feel like reading documentation to do anything with it in the immediate...but maybe a fun project for a rainy day. strudel.cc
